 An novelist imaginative writing a about amateur spy - chasing thriller , might . invent a Clifford Stoll but it unlikely 's
 It also 's unnecessary .
 Amateur spy - chaser Clifford Stoll a person real , or , a surreal person as he put it might waggishly is .
 He 37 , an , astronomer with impressive credentials and something of a genius at making computers do his bidding is .
 He described once himself , as a `` Berkeley Hippie '' and played ; the obligatory , ragged jeans a thicket of long hair and rejection of all things conventional , including formal marriage to his `` '' sweetheart , Martha Matthews for , a time , at least role well .
