 The Germans West then and finally found Markus Hess took over .
 Eventually , Mr. Stoll invited to both CIA the and NSA to brief on computer theft high - ranking officers was .
 He savored the humor of his uncombed appearance among these buttoned - up chaps .
 Back in Berkeley , . he violently scolded by a left - wing lady friend for consorting with such people was
